<section class="explanation">
  <h1 class="section-title">Country Club Rules</h1>
  <h2>Welcome to the club!</h2>
  <h3>Here are some tips to help you navigate</h3>
  <div class="explanation-list">
    <ol>
      <li>Choose a continent or region. This will take you to a list of countries.</li>
      <li>Choose a country. You will find facts and information about the country.</li>
      <li>You can now add this country to a 'wishlist' if you want to visit there, and to 'favourites' if you have already visited!</li>
      <li>Head to the Member's Area to see your wishlists and favourites.</li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>
